Package: adv-speedtest-cli
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, python3 (>= 3.7), python3-requests, python3-websockets, python3-colorama, python3-tqdm
Description: Advanced Speedtest CLI - A cross-platform speedtest utility
 A sophisticated command-line utility for measuring internet speed with precision.
 Engineered for accuracy, optimized for performance, and designed for modern networks.
 .
 Features:
  - Precision Latency Testing with WebSocket-based ping measurement
  - Adaptive Download Testing with multi-threaded parallel connections
  - Dynamic Upload Testing with real-time progress tracking
  - Server diversity with automatic or manual selection
  - Dual-mode authentication for registered users and anonymous testing
  - Color-coded results with performance indicators
  - Real-time progress visualization
  - Configurable concurrency (1-64 connections)
